gin manifest (673 lines)\n    - Infra spec: full Helm values tree, RBAC rules, Dockerfile stages,\n      all 12 CI workflows, Makefile targets, e2e setup (520 lines)\n    \n    Made-with: Cursor\n\n specs/01_go_specification.md             | 755 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++----\n specs/02_python_specification.md         | 711 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++---\n specs/03_infrastructure_specification.md | 598 ++++++++++++++++++++----\n 3 files changed, 1836 insertions(+), 228 deletions(-)\n","exit":0,"description":"Show files changed in the CRD commit","truncated":false},"title":"Show files changed in the CRD commit","time":{"start":1775839623038,"end":1775839623069}}}}
