{"type":"text","timestamp":1775839655308,"sessionID":"ses_287b61ae9ffeRwGS11QpcSqa0Z","part":{"id":"prt_d784a8a04001aBmGXxEp505as8","messageID":"msg_d784a8108001qlPk6b2kFBEmZ8","sessionID":"ses_287b61ae9ffeRwGS11QpcSqa0Z","type":"text","text":"Based on my analysis of the AR-001 change archive:\n\n## AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\n\n**Module:** pkg/apis  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** S\n\n---\n\n### ✅ Completed\n\n1. **Scaffold directory structure**\n   - `pkg/apis/runtime/register.go` - API group registration\n   - `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` - complete directory structure\n\n2. **Type Definitions** (`types.go`)\n   - `AgentRuntimePhase` enum (Pending, Running, Failed, Terminating)\n   - `AgentRuntimeCondition` struct\n   - `CodeInterpreterSpec` struct\n   - `ResourceQuota` struct\n   - `NetworkPolicy` and `NetworkRule` structs\n   - `LifecycleHook` struct\n   - `ContainerSpec` struct\n   - `AgentRuntimeSpec` and `AgentRuntimeStatus` structs\n   - `AgentRuntime` and `AgentRuntimeList` structs\n   - JSON and protobuf tags on all fields\n\n3. **API Registration** (`v1alpha1/register.go`)\n   - `SchemeGroupVersion` definition\n   - `SchemeBuilder` and `AddToScheme` functions\n\n4. **Defaults & Validation**\n   - `defaults.go` - `SetDefaults_AgentRuntime` implementation\n   - `validation.go` - `ValidateAgentRuntime`, `ValidateAgentRuntimeStatusUpdate`, `ValidateAgentRuntimePhase`\n\n5. **CRD Manifest Generation**\n   - `manifests/charts/base/crds/agentruntime.yaml` generated with:\n     - OpenAPI v3 schema validation\n     - Status subresource enabled\n     - AdditionalPrinterColumns (NAME, PHASE, SANDBOX, AGE)\n     - `+genclient`, `+kubebuilder` markers\n\n6. **Code Generation**\n   - `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` - DeepCopy methods generated\n\n7. **Unit Tests**\n   - `types_test.go` - type serialization tests\n   - `defaults_test.go` - defaulting behavior tests\n   - `validation_test.go` - validation rule tests\n\n---\n\n### ⏭️ Deferred\n\n1. **Phase 5: Client Code Generation** (deferred to AR-002 or separate task)\n   - Typed clientset (`pkg/client/clientset/versioned/`)\n   - Listers (`pkg/client/listers/runtime/v1alpha1/`)\n   - Informers (`pkg/client/informers/externalversions/`)\n   - Fake clients for testing\n\n2. **Out of Scope** (per proposal)\n   - Controller implementation → AR-002\n   - Webhook admission controllers → AR-010\n   - Conversion webhooks for version upgrades\n   - CLI commands for AgentRuntime (Python SDK task)\n\n3. **Example YAML** (not yet created)\n   - `examples/agentruntime.yaml` sample resource","time":{"start":1775839655305,"end":1775839655305}}}
